==English==
=== Etymology ===
Contraction of "but her face" (i.e. "Everything about her is great, .... ''but her face''.").

=== Noun ===
'''butterface'''
# (''English, slang'') a person (usually, but not necessarily female) that has a body in great condition, but whose physical attractiveness is lessened by their facial features. 
#:'''Examples:'''
#:*"She is a bit of a butterface"

